root.name: Kyuukyoku Harikiri Stadium Heisei Gannen Han
root.description: OverviewKyuukyoku Harikiri Stadium Heisei Gannen Han is a Baseball game developed by Winky Soft and published by Taito for the Famicom platform. Kyuukyoku Harikiri Stadium Heisei Gannen Han is a part of the Japanese only Kyuukyoku Harikiri Stadium franchise.
